== Icelandic ==

=== Interjection ===

'''sælar og blessaðar'''

# [[hello]], [[greetings]] (''greeting a group of female people'')

=== Also see ===

* [[sæll og blessaður]] (to greet a single male person)
* [[sæl og blessuð]] (to greet a single female person or a mixed male/female group)
* [[sælir og blessaðir]] (to greet a group of male people)

